$ /etc/portage

Some files and directories found in `/etc/portage` include:
  • → Linux/fhs/etc/portage/make_conf[`make.conf`]
  • → Linux/fhs/etc/portage/package_use[`package.use`] (this can apparently be either a file or a directory)
  • `make.profile/` which is a symlink to `→ Linux/fhs/var/db/repos/gentoo/profiles[/var/db/repos/gentoo/profiles]/…`.
